Dalmatian
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an immigrant settler in North Auckland from Dalmatia; one descended from a Dalmatian settler.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
